# Azure SaaS deploy — ARCHIVED

This workflow deployed the PrismRAG **SaaS API** to Azure Container Apps (~$150–225/mo).

The project has pivoted to a **pip-only OSS library** (`prismrag-patch`). Azure resources in `prismrag-rg`
were removed for zero cost. Use:

- **CI:** `.github/workflows/ci.yml` — library tests + build
- **PyPI:** `.github/workflows/publish-pypi.yml` — publish on `v*` tag

To restore SaaS deploy, rename this file back to `deploy.yml` and recreate Azure infra via `infra/deploy.sh`.
